orm{\vx}\leq \lambda_1$. On the one hand, we found that $\max_{\vx} \vx^T A \vx = \lambda_1$. On the other hand, $A\vq_1 = \lambda_1\vq_1$, and thus $\vq_1^TA\vq_1 = \lambda_1$. Therefore, $\vq_1 \in \arg\max_{\vx} \vx^T A \vx$.

